high_descs: Turn around and head towards the recycling bin in the right corner.
Take out the brown ball from the recycling bin.
Turn around, then left, then right around the counter and face the fridge on your left.
Open the fridge and put the brown ball inside, close it, open it, take it out and close it.
Turn left, then left again, then face the kitchen sink on your right.
Put the brown ball inside the kitchen sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold brown ball in the kitchen sink.

place the brown ball inside the fridge to cool, then take it back out
turn to walk over to the kitchen sink

high_descs: Turn around and go to the waste basket to your right.
Take the egg from the waste basket.
Go to the fridge behind you and to your left.
Chill the egg in the fridge.
Turn to the left and go to the sink.
Place the egg in the sink next to the tomato.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled egg in the sink.
